CVE-Description: Windows Print Spooler Remote Code Execution
Title: Windows Print Spooler Remote Code Execution Vulnerability
Solution: Install Microsoft security update KB5005010 to remediate this vulnerability
Results: Print Spooler service vulnerable to RCE

Title: Apache Log4j Remote Code Execution Vulnerability
Solution: Update Apache Log4j to version 2.17.0 or later to remediate this vulnerability
Results: Log4j RCE vulnerability in web application

Title: Zerologon Netlogon Elevation of Privilege Vulnerability
Solution: Install Microsoft security update KB4586794 to remediate this vulnerability

Title: BlueKeep Remote Desktop Protocol RCE Vulnerability
Solution: Disable Remote Desktop Services or install Microsoft security update KB4479138
Results: RDP vulnerability allows remote code execution

Title: Spring4Shell Remote Code Execution Vulnerability
Solution: Update Spring Framework to version 5.3.18 or 5.2.20 to remediate this vulnerability
Results: Spring Framework RCE vulnerability in web app
